column11: How often do you fall sick? (cold/fever/body pain/upset stomach)
column13: Dairy per day? 1 serving = 1 glass of milk OR 1 slice of cheese OR 30 gm paneer
column14: Check the type of Dairy Product that you typically eat/drink:
column15: Quantity of Vegetables per day? 1 serving = 1 cup of uncooked vegetables or ½ cup of cooked vegetables (except potatoes/yam/beans)
column16: Potato/ Sweet Potato/ Beet Root per day
column17: Fruit per day? Juice doesn't count
column19: Whole grain per day? 1 serving = 1 whole wheat bread slice, chapati, bajra roti, or jowar roti OR ½ cup whole wheat pasta, wheat noodles, oatmeal or daliya, brown rice, khichadi, upma, or poha
column20: Sweet Foods per week? (mithais, chocolates, icecreams, cream biscuits, candies, chocolate sauce, cakes, regular soda, sweetened ice tea, lemonade, sports drinks)
column21: Fast and Fried Foods per week? (french fries, fried chicken/ fish, burgers, samosa, pizza, wada pav, chips)
column22: Meat servings per week? 1/2 the size of an adult's palm of fish, chicken, etc
column23: Egg servings per week? 1 serving = 1 whole egg or 2 egg whites
column24: Vegetarian Protein servings per day? 1 serving = ½ cup cooked legumes like beans or chick peas, tofu, soya OR ¾th cup of dal
column25: Nuts per week? 1 serving = approx 4 whole walnuts/12 almonds/9 cashews/15 peanuts, etc.
column26: Do you consume enough water? (minimum 1.5 to 2 litres/day)
column27: Moderate or vigorous exercise per day? (sports, biking, active games involving running and chasing)
column28: Screen time not including homework per day? (TV, Computer use not including homework, Video Games)
column30: Do you eat more when you are under stress?
column31: Do you often skip the breakfast?
column32: Do you check the food labels (low fat/low sugar) before selecting a food item?
column33: What are the topics of nutrition would you like us to address?
column34: Would you like more interactions with our nutritionist?
column35: How disappointed would you be if the nutrition counseling services were stopped tomorrow?
column36: Anything else you would want to share with us?
